---
// Data Disclaimer Component for Project Pages
---

<div class="data-disclaimer bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-4 mb-8 rounded-r-lg">
  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
    <div class="text-2xl">⚠️</div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">Data Disclosure</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
        All data shown in project demonstrations uses <strong>sanitized dummy data</strong>.
        No real client information, company names, or confidential data is displayed.
        Screenshots demonstrate technical capabilities while protecting client confidentiality.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .data-disclaimer {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
